| FR-002 | 查询任务详情/进度 | `GET /api/export/tasks/{taskId}` | PENDING / EXECUTING / COMPLETED / FAILED | AC-002 |
| FR-003 | 下载导出文件 | `GET /api/export/tasks/{taskId}/download` | COMPLETED / EXPIRED | AC-003 |
